@{B}@{u}System Requirements.@{uu}@{ub}

@{fg HIGHLIGHT}SFMV Convertor:@{fg TEXT}
Workbench  3.0  (it  may  work on Workbench 2, but hasn't been tested).  The
ASL.Library, GadTools.Library, and mathstrans.library are required.@{FG SHINE}ą@{FG TEXT}

@{fg HIGHLIGHT}SFMV Player:@{fg TEXT}
Any  AGA  machine  ( The Player requires the AGA chipset to work, it dosen't
matter  which  Workbench  you  have  running  ).   No external libraries are
needed.

@{fg HIGHLIGHT}SFMV Script Generator:@{fg TEXT}
Workbench  3.0  (it  may  work on Workbench 2, but hasn't been tested).  The
ASL.Library and GadTools.Library are required.@{FG SHINE}ą@{FG TEXT}

@{fg HIGHLIGHT}SFMV Animation Utility:@{fg TEXT}
Workbench  3.0  (it  may  work on Workbench 2, but hasn't been tested).  The
ASL.Library is also required.@{FG SHINE}ą@{FG TEXT}


@{FG SHINE}ą@{FG TEXT} These  libraries  are  all standard system libraries so there shouldn't be
any problems.

@ENDNODE
