@{u}                                                                           @{uu}

We have many plans for SFMV.

For  the  format  itself  we  hope  to implement better compression methods.
Increase  the number of colours and screen size.  Allow different timing for
each frame, and the ability to jump to different frames.

For  future plans for the various programs please see the accompanying guide
files.

We are also keen to hear what ideas you would like added.

@ENDNODE
