     The BEST map editor available for all you game/demo writers out there.
     Some of the features... Cut/copy/paste, multiple save/load formats,
     palette editor, highly configurable ( Even includes a screen blanker ),
     attribute control ( Both local and global ), multitasking, etc., and
     best of all, its a real dream to use.
           This utility has been tested on most configurations, and works
     problem free. AGA support is currently limited to 64 colour screens.
